Invocation Name: daily arcana
des:
The world is a confusing place, locked in the tides of great order and chaos. "Daily Arcana" breathes new life into your journey. Using the teachings of the Tarot interpreted by a professional, this skill aims to be your gateway into divination. Each reading of both upright and reversed cards is detailed, containing only the purest and most generous advice to those who seek enlightenment. 

Expand your heart, mind, body and soul. Enlightenment is always just a card away. 

Forces, guide you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
